  "texts": [
    "This integration allowed for the incorporation of up-to-date and contextually appropriate information, significantly improving the factual accuracy of the outputs [3].",
    "The use of retrievers based on dense passage retrieval techniques provided more precise and relevant data, further enhancing the overall performance of RAG systems [4,5].",
    "Subsequent advancements in RAG explored the use of transformer-based retrievers, which leveraged pre-trained models to identify and extract pertinent information from large corpora [6].",
    "Such retrievers demonstrated superior performance compared to traditional search algorithms, as they could understand and process natural language queries more effectively [7].",
    "The integration of transformer-based retrievers with LLMs resulted in more coherent and factually accurate responses, addressing the limitations of previous approaches [8]."
